graph TD
    A[User Query: "Write a short poem about LangGraph"] --> B[Generator Node]
    B -->|Initial Draft| C[Evaluator / Critique Node]
    
    subgraph Iterative Refinement Loop
    C -->|Reads Draft + Original Prompt| D{Is it PERFECT?}
    D -->|No: Error Found| E[Generate Feedback / Critique]
    E -->|Pass Critique back to State| B
    B -.->|Rewrite with Feedback| C
    end
    
    D -->|Yes: Meets Standards| F[END: Release to User]
    
    subgraph Failsafe
    E -.->|Loop Limit Reached| G[END: Release Best Effort]
    end
